snippet.title: Rahul Gandhi Attacks Narendra Modi, Says PM Has Firebombed Poor People With Demonetisation

localized.description:
Soon after Prime Minister Narendra Modi slammed the opposition Congress party during a parivartan rally in Kanpur, Rahul Gandhi  lashed out at PM Modi during while addressing a rally in Jaunpur, Uttar Pradesh saying that demonetisation was a war against people.
